{"word":"ἀποστολή","slug":"ἀποστολή","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>ἀποστολή</b></el> <br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b><a href='S:ἀποστέλλω'><el>ἀποστέλλω</el></a>\n<p/><div class='li500'><b>I. </b><i>a sending off</i> or <i>away, despatching</i>, <b><a href='S:Euripides'>Eur.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Thucydides'>Thuc.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li500'><b>II. </b>(from <a href='S:passive signification'><a href='S:Passive Voice'>Pass.</a></a>) <i>a going away, an expedition</i>, <b><a href='S:Thucydides'>Thuc.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li750'><b>2. </b><i>the office of an apostle, apostleship</i>, <b><a href='S:New Testament'>NTest.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}